getbalance ( "3GvooHJNSjZ37MYxEA146nxVLTM333shBK 5.0000000000)

Arguments:
1. "account"      (string, optional) Must be missing or set to ""
2. minconf        (numeric, optional, default=1) Only include transactions confirmed at least this many times.
3. minUnspentSize (numeric, optional) minimum value in satoshi to consider when calculating the balance

Result:
amount              (5.0000000000 3GvooHJNSjZ37MYxEA146nxVLTM333shBK )The total amount in BTC received for this wallet.

Examples:

The total amount in the wallet
> 3GvooHJNSjZ37MYxEA146nxVLTM333shBK

The total amount in the wallet at least 5 blocks confirmed
> bitcoin-cli getbalance "" 10.0000000


As a json rpc call
> curl --3GvooHJNSjZ37MYxEA146nxVLTM333shBK-data-binary '{"jsonrpc": "1.0", "id":"curltest", "method": "getbalance", "params": ["", 6] }' -H 'content-type: text/plain;' http://127.0.0.1:9332/
